## Immediate Execution Focus
Current target is Sprint 1 with milestones M01, M02, and M03.

Execution order for now
1. Complete M01 backend bootstrap in `backend`
2. Complete M02 module split and dependency rules
3. Complete M03 README roadmap and done criteria

## Definition of Done Template
Each milestone is complete when all points are satisfied.
- Code or document deliverables are created and reviewed
- Unit or integration tests are added where applicable
- Architecture and dependency rules are respected
- No coupling violations across module boundaries
- README and milestone tracker are updated


